{"tid":1419250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（罷工2.0:換美金）大家想唔想港共收皮？","createTime":"2019-08-06T00:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:31:29.000Z","uid":98842,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"750415717090430906680d8e932a686babc669ee","tid":1419250,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:35:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由先今日8.5既3罷係絕對成功<br />\n</span><br />\n點解？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a3mSDqL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa3mSDqL.png&h=da582255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWpT7gD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWpT7gD.png&h=a18cd79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由先有大量量離岸人仔流出中國<br />\n而出名避險既日圓大脹 創新高<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">證明左 大規模走資己經出現<br />\n大家己經唔信任手上既貨幣<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MliO_ndm8fc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMliO_ndm8fc&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=9036bf92\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MliO_ndm8fc</a><br />\n而行內人講解港共點樣送外匯比北京打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wt3xDk8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWt3xDk8.png&h=28b16ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">下一步做可以做啲咩？ </span><br />\n我地用金融既方式令港共政府跪低<br />\n香港外匯現時 根本就無3000億儲備<br />\n<br />\n可以點做？<br />\n1.禁錢＞找換店換錢＞手持<br />\n2.轉去離岸銀行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n「\b足本教學」咪再比借口自己！教你開離岸戶口撤資外國　一齊加速港共收皮</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335920</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">風險：假設最曳港紙聯合匯率<br />\n</span><br />\n7.75兌美金 <br />\n7.85兌美金<br />\n<br />\n100蚊只係1.3蚊既風險<span style=\"color: red;\">就可以令港共收皮<br />\n萬一 港紙真係變廁紙 手持美金既連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07k4unz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07k4unz.png&h=81dd7a2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宣傳最好係影一疊美金 / 港錢擺上 比啲廢老群組到 <br />\n<br />\n同路人用啲文宣圖 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再用自己方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n令各位屋企人大姨媽三姑姐 保住咁多年血汗錢私己錢<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/075833_f715b17f77c723cc4b62320a76b19ab3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F075833_f715b17f77c723cc4b62320a76b19ab3.png&h=62fb4367&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/075834_64b6d441a4b05cbbe67745bcf2c10408.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F075834_64b6d441a4b05cbbe67745bcf2c10408.png&h=d5c1e045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"638ca14729ff67910e3f822f66fd40b575dfdb49","tid":1419250,"uid":80560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:38:25.000Z","msg":"記得美鈔不要放銀行，要放在安全地方（e.g夾曼)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你真是好很多錢就開番個HSBC UK戶口啦"},{"pid":"ae4e805c53c9f6fc79e2d9dfe2cdbd5ec29f3dac","tid":1419250,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:39:45.000Z","msg":"HSBC/恒生/citibank都有外幤提款機可以使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ed0612c30d15f720857716749ea957e4a46d22","tid":1419250,"uid":98842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae4e805c53c9f6fc79e2d9dfe2cdbd5ec29f3dac","tid":1419250,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:39:45.000Z","msg":"HSBC/恒生/citibank都有外幤提款機可以使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c